snippet.title: Rockman DASH 5 Islands: Stage 5-1
snippet.description:
Happy 16th anniversary to Rockman DASH: Great Adventure on 5 Islands!
This gameplay covers the first stage of the final island. This game has now been fully preserved! Check it out here: https://www.rockman-corner.com/2024/02/rockman-dash-great-adventure-on-5.html
